---
// ProcessFlow - Visual 5-step horizontal flow
---

<section class="process-flow-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="process-flow-header">
      <h2>Your Revenue Stack, Compounding</h2>
      <p>With a single source of truth powering your revenue stack, AI can learn what works, scale best practices across teams, and continuously improve messaging, outbound, and sales performance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-flow-visual">
      <svg class="flow-svg" viewBox="0 0 1200 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="flowGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#C8F04A" stop-opacity="0.4" />
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#C8F04A" />
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>

        <!-- Background track -->
        <path
          d="M 120 100 L 1080 100"
          stroke="#2A2A26"
          stroke-width="3"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
        />

        <!-- Animated flow line -->
        <path
          d="M 120 100 L 1080 100"
          stroke="url(#flowGradient)"
          stroke-width="3"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          class="flow-line"
        />

        <!-- Single slow particle -->
        <circle r="5" fill="#C8F04A" class="particle">
          <animateMotion dur="8s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M 120 100 L 1080 100" />
        </circle>

        <!-- Step nodes -->
        <!-- Step 1: Explore -->
        <g class="step-node" transform="translate(120, 100)">
          <circle r="36" fill="#1C1C19" stroke="#C8F04A" stroke-width="2" class="node-circle" />
          <text y="6" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8F04A" font-family="monospace" font-size="18" font-weight="bold">01</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 2: Codify -->
        <g class="step-node" transform="translate(360, 100)">
          <circle r="36" fill="#1C1C19" stroke="#C8F04A" stroke-width="2" class="node-circle" />
          <text y="6" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8F04A" font-family="monospace" font-size="18" font-weight="bold">02</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 3: Connect -->
        <g class="step-node" transform="translate(600, 100)">
          <circle r="36" fill="#1C1C19" stroke="#C8F04A" stroke-width="2" class="node-circle" />
          <text y="6" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8F04A" font-family="monospace" font-size="18" font-weight="bold">03</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 4: Empower -->
        <g class="step-node" transform="translate(840, 100)">
          <circle r="36" fill="#1C1C19" stroke="#C8F04A" stroke-width="2" class="node-circle" />
          <text y="6" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8F04A" font-family="monospace" font-size="18" font-weight="bold">04</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 5: Compound -->
        <g class="step-node" transform="translate(1080, 100)">
          <circle r="36" fill="#1C1C19" stroke="#C8F04A" stroke-width="2" class="node-circle" />
          <text y="6" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8F04A" font-family="monospace" font-size="18" font-weight="bold">05</text>
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps-row">
      <div class="process-step-item">
        <h3>Explore</h3>
        <p>Audit your CRM, data, and systems. Find where revenue leaks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step-item">
        <h3>Codify</h3>
        <p>Define pipeline stages, ARR rules, and clean data standards. Once.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step-item">
        <h3>Connect</h3>
        <p>One AI layer links your tools. Every team pulls from one accurate source of truth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step-item">
        <h3>Empower</h3>
        <p>Coach revenue teams to leverage AI with their tools for smarter execution.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step-item final">
        <h3>Compound</h3>
        <p>New hires inherit everything. New tools plug in. Value accumulates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process-flow-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .process-flow-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .process-flow-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .process-flow-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .process-flow-visual {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .flow-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 200px;
  }

  .flow-line {
    stroke-dasharray: 960;
    stroke-dashoffset: 960;
    animation: drawLine 2s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes drawLine {
    to {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
  }

  .node-circle {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-node:hover .node-circle {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.3));
  }


  .particle {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .process-steps-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-step-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-step-item h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-step-item p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .process-step-item.final h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* Mobile: Stack vertically */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .flow-svg {
      display: none;
    }

    .process-steps-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .process-step-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      text-align: left;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      padding: var(--space-md);
      background: var(--color-bg-raised);
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    }

    .process-step-item.final {
      border-left-color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    .process-step-item::before {
      content: counter(step, decimal-leading-zero);
      counter-increment: step;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 48px;
    }

    .process-step-item.final::before {
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    .process-steps-row {
      counter-reset: step;
    }

    .process-step-item h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    }
  }

  /* Tablet: 3 + 2 layout */
  @media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .process-steps-row {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .process-step-item:nth-child(4),
    .process-step-item:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .flow-svg {
      max-height: 150px;
    }
  }
</style>
